157
00:32:39,000 --> 00:32:41,200
Mmm.

158
00:32:43,733 --> 00:32:46,933
My condolences, ma´am.

159
00:33:08,733 --> 00:33:11,267
- Anthony?
- Mmm.

160
00:33:14,333 --> 00:33:19,800
Come on, I´m gonna take you home.
Okay. Come on.

161
00:33:29,400 --> 00:33:32,933
<i>Earlier today the FBI confirmed</i>

162
