<i>that the plane crash on the Washington
Beltway was caused by a bomb.</i>

163
00:33:40,000 --> 00:33:45,533
<i>Since then, airports around the US
have been on heightened alert.</i>

164
00:33:45,733 --> 00:33:53,267
